Hey, Gemma,
you wanted to see me?

15:45.031 --> 15:47.381
Malcolm?
What are you doing here?

15:47.424 --> 15:50.558
I thought that I would come by
and, uh, surprise you.

15:50.601 --> 15:52.212
Oh, gotta go.

15:52.255 --> 15:54.823
Mrs. Murphy got bit
by the class turtle again.

15:54.866 --> 15:57.043
It is hard to go back to lettuce
when you've tasted blood.

