So, what's going on?

16:02.222 --> 16:04.702
Well, I, um...
I've been thinking a lot

16:04.746 --> 16:08.054
about the idea of
you moving to France.

16:08.097 --> 16:09.403
And there's
something that I...

16:09.446 --> 16:10.926
I'm not going.

16:10.970 --> 16:13.755
What? Really?

16:13.798 --> 16:15.148
Really.

16:15.191 --> 16:17.411
What made you
decide to stay?

16:17.454 --> 16:22.155
Well, the more I thought
about going,

16:22.198 --> 16:25.810
the more I realized I don't
want to mess up my life.

16:25.854 --> 16:28.596
Mess up your life?

16:28.639 --> 16:33.079
Yeah. I mean,
I know going to Paris

16:33.122 --> 16:35.516
is something I've always
dreamed of,

16:35.559 --> 16:38.562
but I'm just afraid that

16:38.606 --> 16:41.217
if I give up
everything here to go,

16:41.261 --> 16:43.524
and then it doesn't work out,

16:43.567 --> 16:45.526
I'd never forgive myself.

16:49.747 --> 16:52.707
You know, I know
exactly how you feel.

16:54.187 --> 16:56.058
Which is why you have to go.

16:58.408 --> 17:00.019
What?

17:00.062 --> 17:03.109
Look, Sofia, nothing
would make me happier

17:03.152 --> 17:04.675
than if you stayed.

17:04.719 --> 17:07.939
But you can't let
being afraid stop you

17:07.983 --> 17:09.941
from going after
something that you want.

17:09.985 --> 17:13.423
'Cause if you do,
you'll always be wondering

17:13.467 --> 17:15.817
"what if?" And...

17:15.860 --> 17:18.689
that's no way to live.

17:18.733 --> 17:21.257
I'm gonna miss you.

17:23.129 --> 17:25.348
Yeah, no, I, uh...

17:25.392 --> 17:27.350
I miss you already.

