I don't know
what Dad's talking about.

18:00.949 --> 18:02.385
My camerawork is great.

18:02.429 --> 18:04.126
I mean sure,
the slow motion didn't work,

18:04.170 --> 18:05.954
but that was only
in the flashbacks.

18:07.651 --> 18:09.958
And there was nothing
wrong with my acting.

18:10.001 --> 18:11.655
Although...

18:11.699 --> 18:14.049
falling out of the wheelchair
might have been a bit much.

18:16.617 --> 18:18.184
Yeah, in hindsight,

18:18.227 --> 18:20.925
maybe I shouldn't have
licked that wrench.

